com.software.reuze

Class vc_ColorNamesInt

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.software.reuze.vc_ColorNamesInt
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    vc_ColorNames

    public class vc_ColorNamesInt
extends Object
    HTML color names. It's intended use is for parsing a name and return the corresponding color or return a name for a given color.
    Author:
    Adrian Ber, from package com.greef.ui project jcalendar @koders.com, modified by R. Cook for libgdx
